                     <interp inst="t18431211-286-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 2 pairs of trowsers, value 17<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18431211-name-87" type="victimName">
